Sigdo Koppers Confirms Negotiations to Sell CTI Unit in Chile

-- B y   E d u a r d o   T h o m s o n
-- 
2011-08-17T18:12:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-17/sigdo-koppers-confirms-negotiations-to-sell-cti-unit-in-chile.html
Sigdo Koppers SA, a Chilean holding
company, confirmed its in negotiations with an undisclosed group
to sell its home appliances unit CTI Cia. Tecno Industrial SA.  Negotiations are in “advanced” stage and there is still
no definitive agreement, Sigdo Koppers said in a statement
posted on the website of  Chile ’s securities regulator.  To contact the reporter on this story:
